        public static boolean isConflict(boolean[][] placement,
                                 int row,
                                 int col,
                                 int orientation,
                                 int longGridNum)
        Parameters:
        placement - for placement of ship
        row - if the ship is placed vertical
        col - if ship is placed horizontal
        orientation - checks whether the sip placed in vertically or horizontally.
        longGridNum - checks the grid of the ship.
        Returns:
        True if the ship is not conflict with other ships, otherwise return false.
